#CHIP HuC6280
#CLOCK 7159090

; HuC6280 (Hudson Soft) Wavetable Test
;
; The HuC6280 is the sound chip used in the PC Engine / TurboGrafx-16.
; It has 6 channels: 5 wavetable channels and 1 noise channel.
; Each wavetable channel can use one of 32 built-in waveforms.
;
; Tests:
; - Wavetable playback with different waveforms
; - Volume control
; - Pitch modulation

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 1: Sine wave wavetable
c4 .

; Channel 2: Square wave wavetable
d4 .

; Channel 3: Sawtooth wavetable
e4 .

; Channel 4: Triangle wavetable
f4 .

; Channel 5: Pulse wavetable
g4 .

r4

; All 5 wavetable channels together
c4 & d4 & e4 & f4 & g4 .

r4

; Wavetable pitch sweep
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 .

r2

#END
